      {
        "id": 3100157,
        "name": "Mark Lewis",
        "username": "Mark_Lewis",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/c67d28/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-02-10T22:23:27.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I understand that Bollinger recommended the other way around. The regular bottles can be aged, but the RD bottles should be drunk immediately.</p>\n<p>I have never been able to conduct a good enough experiment to know if that is true though!</p>",
        "post_number": 2,
