        "created_at": "2021-02-11T02:25:00.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"168353\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>People say this, but if the disgorgement is done well, I don\u2019t think it\u2019s true. I drank a not very recently R.D. 1973 Bollinger last year and it was great.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>agree that the wine is fine down the road.</p>",
