        "cooked": "<p>The logic applies to Port. LBV are early drinkers and early bottled VP keeps for decades.</p>\n<p>Of course, William is going to tell us about an amazing 1883 LBV that he recently tasted.  <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/a/a7452fcd8e675af869f8da01174474a545b03944.gif\" width=\"56\" height=\"37\" alt=\"[rofl.gif]\" title=\"rofl\"></p>\n<p>Edit: Just saw Brad\u2019s incredibly complex reply. Wow. How lucky we are to have Brad and William on WB.</p>",
